pine_reflectance_exposed_A: Directional - hemispherical reflectance of adaxial (upper-facing) Scots Pine needles taken from sun-exposed canopy position.
pine_reflectance_exposed_B: Directional - hemispherical reflectance of abaxial (lower-facing) Scots Pine needles taken from sun-exposed canopy position.
pine_reflectance_shaded_A: Directional - hemispherical reflectance of adaxial (upper-facing) Scots Pine needles taken from shaded canopy position.
pine_reflectance_shaded_B: Directional - hemispherical reflectance of abaxial (lower-facing) Scots Pine needles taken from shaded canopy position.
